; DISPLAY.DEF - module definition para Windows 1.x
; AUTO-GENERATED desde ATTDEB.DRV (NE entry/relocation tables)

LIBRARY     DISPLAY
DESCRIPTION 'DISPLAY : 120, 96, 80 : AT&T Display Enhancement Board'
EXETYPE     WINDOWS
STUB        'WINSTUB.EXE'

CODE        PRELOAD FIXED
DATA        PRELOAD FIXED SINGLE

IMPORTS
